quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  37,77,"Mana nikhukhola olwibulo lulwe okhutoong’a."
  37,78,"Mana nikhumuleshela ifuma indayi khubetsa inyuma wuwe."
  37,79,"Omuleembe kube khu Nuhu mushialo shioosi."
  37,80,"Toto endio nilwa khurunganga abakholi bamalayi."
  37,81,"Toto ye ali Mubasumba befu Abasuubili."
  37,82,"Mana Abandi abo nikhubasishia mumatsi."
  37,83,"Ne toto Ibrahim yali mumukaanda kukwe."
  37,84,"Olwa yetsela Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi nende omwoyo kukwe kwoosi."
  37,85,"Olwa yaboolela papa wuwe nende Abandu bebe mbu: “Ni shina shiamulamaanga?"
  37,86,"Eminyasaye chiobubeyi echilali Nyasaye nichiamwenyanga?"
  37,87,"Mupariranga shina Nyasaye Omulesi webilonje bioosi?”"
  37,88,"Mana nasitia tsimoni okhuhenga tsing’ining’ini."
  37,89,"Naboola mbu: “Toto esie endwala.”"
  37,90,"Nabo nibamulekha nibamufutarira omukongo."
  37,91,"Mana nabwondela eminyasaye chiabu. Nachiboolela mbu: “Shichila shina shimuliitsanga tawe?"
  37,92,"Mubeele murie wamulalomalomanga tawe?”"
  37,93,"Mana nachikalukhanila nachikhupa nomukhono omulunji."
  37,94,"Mana nibamwitsila lwangu lwangu."
  37,95,"Naboola mbu: “Enywe mulaamanga ebindu bia mwiraanyanga abeene?"
  37,96,"Ne Nyasaye niye wabaloonga halala nende akamukholanga ako.""
  37,97,"Nibaboola mbu: “Muumbashile eshiumbashe mana mumusukune mumulilo.”"
  37,98,"Kho benya okhumukholela amabii, halali nikhubakhola bo okhuba ba hasi muno."
  37,99,"Ne naboola mbu: “Toto esie ewuya enzia ewa Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, Ye alalunjisia.""
  37,100,""Ewe Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, mbelesia ulia uli mubakholi bamalayi.""
  37,101,"Mana nikhumuboolera koomwikhoyo, komwana omwihotselefu muno."
  37,102,"Olwa yoola eshichelo shiokhuchenda ninaye, yamuboolela mbu: “Ewe mwana wanje, toto esie endutsi mumaloro mbu ekhusinzanga, kho hengamwo, olola orie?” Naboola mbu: “Ewe papa wanje, khola shinga oloomesibungwa, witsa okhuunyoola Nyasaye nachama, nendi mubalia befwiilanga.”"